      "heading": null,
      "description": "Boil the broccoli in a pot of salted boiling water for 3-4 mins until it’s just about cooked. Then remove it and allow it to cool."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Preheat your oven to 180°C. Season your chicken breasts generously with salt and pepper. Place your breasts onto a baking tray and get them in the oven for 25 mins. Allow them to cool once cooked – the salad doesn’t need to be warm. Add the bacon in for the last 10 mins until crispy."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Heat up your quinoa according to the package instructions."
    },
    {
