    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Add it all to a bowl with the quinoa."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Make the dressing with oil, lemon juice, mustard, and honey. Mix it all up until emulsified and coat the salad."
    },
    {
